================================================================================
CURRENT ISSUE & BLOCKERS
================================================================================

Docker build for csrs-daemon is failing due to:
  Error: Playwright browser installation (chromium) failing
  Root cause: Missing font packages in Debian Trixie (ttf-unifont, ttf-ubuntu-font-family)
  
  Error line: RUN playwright install chromium --with-deps (Dockerfile.daemon:37)
  Exit code: 100
  
  This is a known issue with Playwright and newer Debian base images.

POTENTIAL FIXES:
1. Replace Playwright dependencies with pre-built Chromium from system packages
2. Use a different base image (Ubuntu-based instead of Debian slim)
3. Skip --with-deps and install fonts manually before playwright
4. Pre-build the chromium installation in a separate layer

